'''The Gall Enclave jetpacks''' were a line of [[Jetpack/Legends|jetpacks]] used by the forces of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] enclave on [[Gall/Legends|Gall]]. [[Dash Rendar/Legends|Dash Rendar]] stole one during the [[Battle of Gall]], using it to negotiate the treacherous terrain of the planet's [[Smuggler's Canyon|canyons]] and integrating it into his normal equipment for use in later [[Battle over Coruscant|missions]].

